ActTerritorial Lands Act
PrecisORDER RESPECTING THE WITHDRAWAL FROM DISPOSAL OF CERTAIN LANDS IN THE NORTHWEST TERRITORIES (EDÉHZHIE (HORN PLATEAU), N.W.T.) - which provides for (a) the repeal of the Withdrawal Order made by Order in Council P.C. 2002-1805 of October 24, 2002, and (b) the withdrawal from disposal of approximately 2.5 million hectares of land situated in the vicinity of Horn Plateau, in the Northwest Territories.
